properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Mexico Beach out 20 NM; Coastal Waters From  Ochlockonee River to Apalachicola FL out to 20 Nm; Apalachee Bay or Coastal Waters From Keaton Beach to Ochlockonee River Fl out to 20 Nm; Coastal Waters from Mexico Beach to Apalachicola out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 12 at 2:01PM EST until January 13 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one quarter mile or
less.

* WHERE...Nearshore Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County
line to the Ochlockonee River out 20 nautical miles, and
Apalachee Bay or Coastal Waters From Keaton Beach to
Ochlockonee River FL out to 20 Nm.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ Monday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ MONDAY
